    <p>Whether you choose to have it on its own, pair it with a glass of light-bod­ied red wine or cham­pagne, or let it play the per­fect ac­com­pa­ni­ment to a healthy salad of juicy cherry toma­toes and rocket leaves, bur­rata cheese is as ver­sa­tile as it is de­li­cious.</p>
    <p>And you can now get your fix of lus­cious, creamy good­ness at a pro­mo­tional price! Now at $6.65 (U.P. $6.95), Gioiella’s fresh bur­rata (100g) brings a per­fect blend of con­trast­ing tex­tures to the palate — from the soft­ness of its outer shell to its molten cen­tre.</p>
    <p>The item is ex­clu­sive to FairPrice Hyper and Finest stores.</p>

